{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762172622834","path":null,"data":{"id":1904,"title":"Manulife:新產品推出「富足自主年金計劃」及「財摯系列」","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1682406648981,"tags":["宏利保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一、<strong>新產品推出-「富足自主年金計劃」</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.宏利保險於<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>2023年4月24日</strong></span>誠意推出「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>富足自主年金計劃</strong></span>」。此計劃提供保證和非保證的每月入息，年金期可<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>高達25年</strong></span>。最早入息開始年度為繳清保費後度。此外，計劃可靈活更改入息的開始年度，但須為繳清保費後的10年內。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-04-25/d43215f33bd349ea9070928e4858ae9a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"354\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.於<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">2023年4月24日至2023年6月30日</span></strong>成功投保<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>富足自主年金計劃</strong></span>，可享<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>高達15%</strong></span>首年保費折扣優惠。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、<strong>新產品推出-定期保費選項的「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">財摯傳承保障計劃</span>」及「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">財摯家傳保障計劃</span>」</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.宏利保險於<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>2023年4月24日</strong></span>誠意推出定期保費選項的「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>財摯傳承保障計劃</strong></span>」及「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>財摯家傳保障計劃</strong></span>」。以每一受保人計算，所有「財摯家傳保障計劃」的無需醫療核保總保費為<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>美元1,000,000<span style=\"color: #000000;\">/</span>港元8,000,000</strong></span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.於<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>2023年4月24日至2023年6月30日</strong></span>內申請的保費繳付期為3年或以上的「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>財摯傳承保障計劃</strong></span>」/「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>財摯家傳保障計劃</strong></span>」，可享有<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>高達15%</strong></span>首年保費折扣優惠：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-04-24/a1e49f8e9ad44516b91c7a0f6ab959c1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"396\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 三、為把握高資產淨值客戶對人壽保障產品需求的市場機遇，宏利保險欣然於<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>2023年4月24日</strong></span><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">推出</span><strong>「盈傳創富保障計劃2」的全新客戶推廣免費附加保障-身故賠償加強保</strong></span>，以及<span style=\"color: #236fa1;\"><strong>紅利分配更新</strong></span>，以強化產品的保證身故賠償保障及非保證預期價值。現行整付保費10%折扣優惠己經終止，亦不能同時享有以上及新推廣及紅利分配更新。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 四、定期保費選項的「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>財摯傳承保障計劃</strong></span>」及「<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><strong>財摯家傳保障計劃</strong></span>」已於<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>2023年4月24日</strong></span><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\"><strong>新增至宏利保證利息迎春推廣的指定儲蓄計劃</strong></span>。此外，推廣期將會<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>延長至2023年5月31日</strong></span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify;\">詳情請參閱附件。</span></span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"NewsFlash.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-04-25/e6466f034c774b3eade6e89068ccf6ab.pdf","uploadTime":1682389078139,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"富足自主年金計劃推廣計劃.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-04-25/98fc657780d944bcbcf5dbcba283cb1c.pdf","uploadTime":1682389083613,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"財摯系列推廣計劃.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-04-25/130cafaa5e6f4748abf77f72e7f5dc31.pdf","uploadTime":1682389092861,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"提前繳付保費安排申請表.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-04-25/b5cef5123d274f9ea4b8b29e6f241dc5.pdf","uploadTime":1682389117341,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"2022紅利分配調整參考手冊.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-04-25/890357d961484e6fa7b82758c2863072.pdf","u